\newlabel{tab:main}{{1}{6}{Comprehensive results on 9{,}188-triple biomedical KG. Hit@10 from multi-seed (3 seeds $\times $ 20 pairs); StrictFaith reported as mean$\pm $std over 3 seeds; faithfulness from fair evaluation (10 pairs, post-hoc path extraction); KGQA from 10 single-hop questions. The $p$-column reports a query-level paired permutation test ($n{=}20$ queries) of KG-SCoRE vs.\ each baseline on Hit@10. Best in \textbf {bold}; $\dagger $ indicates $p{<}0.05$.\relax }{table.caption.23}{}}
